<signature>
platform
</signature>
ゲームが何のプラットフォームで動いているかを返す（読み取り専用）。
Use this property if you absolutely need to do some platform dependent work.
SA: [[RuntimePlatform]].
CONVERTEXAMPLE
BEGIN EX
	function Start () {
		if (Application.platform == RuntimePlatform.WindowsPlayer)
			print ("Do something special here!");
	}
END EX